HEADWORD: Sleepish
<hw>Sleep"ish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Disposed to sleep;
sleepy; drowsy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Your <qex>sleepish</qex>, and more than <qex>sleepish</qex>,
security.</q> <rj><qau>Ford.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sleepless</ent>⟦br⟧
